## Use the following, finish writing the `sort` function

<pre class="code javascript" >
function red(){ ... }
function green(){ ... }
function blue(){ ... }
function unknown(){ ... }
</pre>

* if the argument `color` equals 'red', then call `red()`
* if the argument `color` equals 'green', then call `green()`
* if the argument `color` equals 'blue', then call `blue()`
* for any other value, simply call `unknown()`

